# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# COMMENTS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# This gitignore protects:
# 1. Terraform state files containing sensitive infrastructure details
# 2. Variable files with actual passwords and secrets
# 3. Environment files with configuration
# 4. IDE and OS-specific files
# 5. Any backup or temporary files that might contain sensitive data
#
# Always review files before committing to ensure no secrets are included!